{"tid":530951,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陰 陽 屎 忽 鬼 健 吾：大 阪 觀 光 客 超 過 一 千 萬，我 的 眼 光 被 旅 客 證 實 了","createTime":"2018-01-16T09:51:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-17T06:21:15.000Z","uid":67840,"like":1,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"8c38e2fad76f2cbe11fef530defa96fd75db9bc7","tid":530951,"uid":67840,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T09:51:52.000Z","msg":"健吾：<br />\n<br />\n十年前， 鮑偉聰 先生邀我寫書，寫日本，我說，不如寫一本關於 大阪 的城市文化書。<br />\n<br />\n然後，就出了那一本書。2000本，全沒有了。也沒有再印。<br />\n<br />\n現在，有人在圖書館找到那本書，然後跟著去，吃每一家餐廳，都讚不絕口。<br />\n<br />\n但我還記得，十年前，文化界有些人對外面書，說我沒有品味，大阪不及東京好，大阪像深圳，又土又吵又髒。<br />\n<br />\n我說，這才是新開發地區。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2017年，大阪的觀光客，超過1000萬人次。<br />\n<br />\n1000萬人次。<br />\n<br />\n我的眼光，被旅客用身體用鈔票證實了。<br />\n<br />\n多謝大家。"},{"pid":"af2e4688c16484164aa83fee1e55b38849250804","tid":530951,"uid":4574,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T09:56:10.000Z","msg":"真是荒謬，把自己看得那麼高"},{"pid":"f2d734d20d9e17a2d970b03bedf2b71e9624e9d3","tid":530951,"uid":121473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T09:56:27.000Z","msg":"咁好記憶力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9e663e3a1e4f907be426567c69993c5f14b4572","tid":530951,"uid":67840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T09:57:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真是荒謬，把自己看得那麼高</blockquote><br />\n要不是.jpg"},{"pid":"a437078b0bd8e8f72d3327fd4e463a9d2ce16746","tid":530951,"uid":41411,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T09:59:47.000Z","msg":"你當自己邊撚個?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b0d3594cbb08308f84a8743186acb403be97a96","tid":530951,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T10:00:58.000Z","msg":"好小器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36434d0035599a533a4229ef8560b84ecdfeddd0"